description: Tacos Rick-O is treating the streets of Charlotte to fresh, tasty, and traditional Tacos and Tortas that local foodies love so much, they’re shoutin’ their praises all over social media. You too will love their menu of delicious Trompo Tacos with Flank Steak or Al Pastor in fresh Flour or Corn Tortillas, Tequila Shrimp Tacos, and deliciously authentic Mexican Burgers. Come seek out Tacos Rick-O because this fantastic food will make your week!
name: Tacos Rick-O
